<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Open+Sans:ital,wght@0,400;0,600;0,700;1,400&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <title>Document</title>
    <style>
      
html,
body {
  background-color: #eaeaea;
  font: 400 1rem/1.625rem "Open Sans", sans-serif;
}

.transition {
  transition: .3s cubic-bezier(.3, 0, 0, 1.3)
}

.card {
  background-color:#fef6fa;
  height: 900px;
  width: 500px;
  position: absolute;
  margin: auto;
  top: 0;
  bottom: 0;
  left: 0;
  right: 0;
  box-shadow: 0px 0px 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.3);
 
}
.gg{
  display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
      padding-left:40px;
    padding-right:40px;
    color: black;

}
.bb{
  text-align: center;
  color: black;
}

.otp{
    justify-content: center;
    text-align: center;
    color:rgb(210, 41, 145);
    margin-top: 20px;
    padding-left: 40px;
    padding-right: 40px;
}
.gg1{
  display: flex;
    justify-content: left;
    padding-left:40px;
    padding-right:40px;
    color: rgb(0, 0, 0);
}

table, th, td {
  color: black;
  
  margin-top: 30px;
  margin-left: auto;
  margin-right: auto;
}
th, td {
text-align: center;
  border-radius: 10px;
  border-style: double;
}

    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="card">
      
<img style= "margin-left: 40%; margin-top:10px;" src = "https://template.preview.drcstudio.co.in/logo2.png" alt="" width="100px" height="100px" class="center">

        <div class="bb">
        <h1 style="font-family: arial">Anya Healthcare</h1>
        </div>
        <div class="gg1">
          <h1 style="font-family: arial">Hi <b>{{name}}</b>,</h1>
          </div>
          <div class="gg1">
            <p style="font-size:120%">The Health Insurance Marketplace has four levels of health plans - Bronze, Silver, Gold, and Platinum - are differentiated based on their actuarial value </p>
            </div>
            <div class="gg1">
            <p style="font-size:120%">On average, <b>Bronze</b> plan will cover 60% of covered medical expenses, and your share will be the remaining 40%. </p>
            </div>
            <div class="gg1">
            <p style="font-size:120%">On average, <b>Silver</b> plan will cover 70% of covered medical expenses, and your share will be the remaining 30%. </p>
            </div>
            <div class="gg1">
            <p style="font-size:120%">On average, <b>Gold</b> plan will cover 80% of covered medical expenses, and your share will be the remaining 20%. </p>
            </div>
            <div class="gg1">
            <p style="font-size:120%">On average, <b>Platinum</b> plan will cover 90% of covered medical expenses, and your share will be the remaining 10%. </p>
            </div>
            
              
              <div class="gg1" >
                <p style="font-size:120%">If you did not request this, please contact your healthcare center.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="gg1">
                  <p style="font-size:120%">Thanks,<b>{{name}}.</b></p>
                                  
                </div>
      </div>
      
</body>
</html>